{
  "element": {
    "type": "container",
    "sourceTag": "div",
    "children": [
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "HOW TO PLAY"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-title"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-2"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Gameplay"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-3"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Watch the panels light up in sequence, then repeat the pattern. Each round adds one more step. Miss too many and it is game over!"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-4"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Browser Controls"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-5"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Click panels to select them. Press 1-9 keys for quick panel select. ESC to pause. R to rematch."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-6"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "VR Controls"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-7"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Point controller at panels and pull trigger. B button to pause. Laser pointer for menu buttons."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-8"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Modes"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-9"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Classic: Growing sequence. Speed: Faster each round. Reverse: Repeat backwards. Rush: 60 second time limit. Zen: No lives. Daily: Same puzzle for everyone. Survival: One mistake. Marathon: Reach level 50."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-10"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Layouts"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-11"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Choose 4 to 12 panels. More panels = harder to remember which one lit up!"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-12"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Scoring"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-13"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Points per correct hit increase with level and combo. Complete rounds for bonus points. Build combos for multipliers!"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-14"
      },
      {
        "type": "container",
